POST documents/medline/_search
{
  "query": {
    "bool": {
      "must": [
        {
          "term": {
            "conceptlist": "tid1703"
          }
        },
        {
          "term": {
            "conceptlist": "tid1805"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "fields": [
    "title",
    "authors"
  ]
}

MUST: ==> both tids have to occur in the conceptlist

----------------------------------------------------------------

